Introduction
=====================================

Fontacts is a simple application for managing your contacts, it covers the techniques and design fundamentals required to create modern web applications. 
The application looks at the fundamentals of building web applications using the following technologies:

- Play Framework (An MVC framework for building web applications in Scala and Java)

- MongoDB (A NoSQL Database system)

- Salat (Simple Serialization with MongoDB and Scala)

- EmberJS (A javascirpt framework)

- And of course Html, Css, and the ubiquitous JQuery.
